# Peggy UI — MUI + Lovable

UI stack is MUI only — never add Tailwind.

**Lovable reference:** https://source-sense-lab.lovable.app

- Match dashboard + sidebar exactly (`AppShell`, `DashboardPage`, `theme/peggyTheme.ts`).
- Inner pages: `PageHeader` + MUI `Paper` + `peggyTheme` tokens (`eyebrowSx`, `monoSx`, `cardHoverSx`).
- Fonts: Inter + JetBrains Mono via `next/font` in `app/layout.tsx`.

## Demo vs live data

When corpus is empty, use Lovable placeholder stats (142 papers, 94% indexed) and the demo activity feed.

When corpus has data, show live API data instead.

Workspace copy: `NEXT_PUBLIC_WORKSPACE_TITLE`, `NEXT_PUBLIC_WORKSPACE_FOCUS` in `apps/web/.env.local`.

See `Loveable.md` for component mapping.
